<div class="row" id="about_page">
  <div class="large-6 columns" id="about_page_section">
    <h1>ABOUT OMAWHO</h1>
      <p><b>This is who we are.</b> So many different faces make up this active, brilliant and (surprisingly) small community. <%= @site_title %> is a proud announcement of membership in that community.</p>
      <p><b>Questions?</b></p>
      <p>Email Team Omawho:<br />
      <b><a href="mailto:team@omawho.com" target="_blank">team@omawho.com</a></b></p>
      <hr/>
      <h2>BUT HOW DO I USE IT?</h2>
      <p>So you're at Big Omaha, bumping into everyone you've ever shaken hands with. Forgot someone's name? It happens to all of us. Next time, skim Omawho in the parking lot beforehand.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="large-6 columns">
    <div id="mobile_image_heading">
      <hr/>
      <h2>MEET A FEW FRIENDLY FACES</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row about_page_photos" id="face-display">
      <% @users.each do |user| %>
        <div class="large-6 columns">
          <%= link_to (image_tag((user.images.first ? user.images.first : "user-avatar.jpg"), :alt => "This is you! (?)", :id => "testimage", :class => "img-polaroid")), view_profile_path(user.username) %>
        <div style="display: none;"><%= user.first_name %> <%= user.last_name %></div>
        <div style="display: none;"><%= link_to 'Show', user %></div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

</div> <!-- End Container -->